description: This file defines an interface 'ITypeScriptParser' that specifies a contract for parsing TypeScript class source code into structured information. It includes documentation comments describing its purpose and the main method 'ParseAsync' for parsing source strings asynchronously.

classes.name: ITypeScriptParser
classes.description: An interface that provides a contract for parsing TypeScript source code into structured class information.

methods.name: ParseAsync
methods.description: Asynchronously parses a TypeScript class source string and returns structured information about the class. May utilize regex for simple parsing and external tooling for complex scenarios.
